sub_questions: Which rows have Arena equal to 'A'?
Which rows have League equal to 'SL'?
Which rows have Match number greater than 16?
What is the Result value for rows matching all three conditions?

unit_annotations.Date & Time ( CET ): date and time in Central European Time format dd.mm.yy, HH:MM
unit_annotations.Team and Score: team names and scores in format 'Team1 - Team2, Score1-Score2'

format_notes: Match column contains numeric values as strings
Arena column contains single letter codes (A or H for Away or Home)
League column contains abbreviated league codes (FM, SL, EL, CBA)
Result column contains score pairs separated by en-dash (–)

constraints: Match must be numeric and greater than 16
derived_filters: Convert Match column from string/object to numeric for comparison
Filter where Arena == 'A' AND League == 'SL' AND Match > 16
output_format_requirements: Return the Result value(s) matching all filter conditions
If multiple matches exist, return all Results
If no matches exist, indicate no results found
